quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,Alif-Lâm-Mîm
  29,2,"Ingaba abantu (aba) bacinga ukuba baza kuyekwa na kuba besithi: “Siyakholwa”, bangavavanywa"
  29,3,"Kodwa Sabavavanya abo bangaphambili kunabo, kwaye uAllâh Uza kwenza bacace abo banyanisekileyo, Abenze bacace nabo bangamaxoki"
  29,4,Makube mhlawumbi abo benza izenzo zokungcola bacinga ukuba bangaphuncula kuThi? Ingcolile (indlela) abagweba ngayo
  29,5,"Nabani na onethemba lokudibana noAllâh inene ixesha (elibekwe) nguAllâh liyeza. Yaye Yena nguSokuva, uSolwazi"
  29,6,"Ke kaloku lowo uzabalazayo, uzabalazela kuphela ukusindisa isiqu sakhe. Inene uAllâh Akadingi nto emaphakadeni"
  29,7,"Abo bakholwayo benze izenzo ezilungileyo ngenene Thina Siya kuzisusa izenzo zabo ezigwenxa kubo, Sibavuze kananjalo kangangoko kulungileyo bakwezayo"
  29,8,"Kananjalo Siyalele ukulunga emntwini kubazali (bakhe) kodwa ukuba bakuyalela ukuba wayamanise (amahlulelane) kuM (Mna Allâh) ongenalwazi wena ngawo, ungabathobeli. KukuM apho ukubuyela kwenu kukhoyo, yaye Ndiya kunazisa ngoko nakwenzayo"
  29,9,"Abo bakholwayo, benze izenzo ezilungileyo Siya kubangenisa ngenene phakathi kwabangamalungisa (ePaladesi)"
  29,10,"Ebantwini kukho abo bathi: “Siyakholwa kuAllâh,” kodwa athi omnye kubo esakuhlelwa bububi ngenxa ka- Allâh, bayithathe loo ntlungu yenziwe ngabantu (kubo) ngokungengathi sisohlwayo sika-Allâh. Kodwa xa uloyiso lufika luvela eNkosini yakho, bathi: “Inene thina besikunye nani.”Ayingo-Allâh na Ongoyena Waziyo ngoko kusezifubeni zezidalwa"
  29,11,"Ke kaloku uAllâh Uza kwenza bacace abo bakholwayo, kwaye Uza kubenza babonakale nabahanahanisi"
  29,12,"Abo bangakholwayo bathi kwabo bakholwayo: “Landelani indlela yethu, thina siya kuzithwala izono zenu.” Kodwa abayi kuthwala nento le kwezo zono zabo. Eneneni bona ngamaxoki"
  29,13,"Kodwa baza kuthwala eyabo imithwalo neminye imithwalo kunye naloo mithwalo yabo, yaye baza kubuzwa ngokwenene ngeMini yoVuko ngoko bakuqambayo"